cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.CE 

This paper discusses the integration of edge computing resources and cloud services to provide seamless service provisioning, which falls under the category of networked and distributed systems (cs.NI) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The paper also proposes a large-scale linear programming problem to efficiently schedule and utilize resources, which can be categorized under data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the cost reduction achieved by the proposed model, which can be categorized under computer engineering (cs.CE).
